flowchart TB
    BA[SlotsContainerBundleAgent]
    REG[TContainerRegistry]
    MOD[SlotsContainerModerator]
    TC[TContainer]
    TS[TSlot]
    RM[RoundManager]
    IW[TIngressWaitingList]
    DW[TDispatchWaitingList]
    RP[ReferencePrecalculator]
    ING[Ingress]
    DSP[Dispatcher]

    BA -->|creates/scales| REG
    BA -->|default empty profile| MOD
    REG -->|indexed containers| MOD
    MOD -->|state/readiness view| RM
    RM -->|ingress-eligible index| IW
    RM -->|dispatch-eligible index| DW
    IW --> RP
    DW --> RP
    REG --> RP
    TC --> TS
    REG --> TC
    RP -->|TIngressAccessRef| ING
    RP -->|TDispatchAccessRef| DSP
    ING -->|places envelope| TS
    DSP -->|exposes envelope| OUT[Output Boundary]
